ing flower path for people to enjoy and take pictures of.\n\nMany locals and tourists come here to relax while enjoying the nature here. People often set up tents and offer others food, snacks and other refreshments. It is a great spot for a run, and you surely should not miss it even if it\'s not in the middle of cherry blossom season. It is a good way of seeing downtown Tokyo but also enjoying the peace and quiet.\n\nIn case you don\'t feel like walking, you can hop into a paddle boat and see the beautiful scenery from the water.\n\nThe moat is a short walk away from the Kudanshita and Hanzonmon metro stations.","provider":null,"translation_provider":null,"link":null,"is_translated":true},"opening_hours_raw":null,"media_count":10,"main_media":{"usage":{"square":"m:47205133","video_preview":null,"portrait":"m:47205133","landscape":"m:47205132"},"media":[{"original":{"size":null,"width":3072,"height":2048},"suitability":["portrait","square"],"url_template":"https://media-cdn.sygictraveldata.com/media/{size}/612664395a40232133447d33247d383437323035313333","created_at":"2017-10-29T08:02:33+0000","source":{"provider":"wikipedia","name":"Wikimedia Commons","external_id":null},"type":"photo","created_by":"53d8a9428f8ff","url":"https://media-cdn.sygictraveldata.com/media/612664395a40232133447d33247d383437323035313333.jpg","quadkey":null,"attribution":{"title_url":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Chidorigafuchi_(3451082281).jpg","license":"CC BY-SA 2.0","other":null,"author_url":"https://www.flickr.com/people/81943113@N00","author":"KimonBerlin","title":"Chidorigafuchi","license_url":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0"},"location":null,"id":"m:47205133"},{"original":{"size":null,"width":3072,"height":2048},"suitability":["landscape"],"url_template":"https://media-cdn.sygictraveldata.com/media/{size}/612664395a40232133447d33247d383437323035313332","created_at":"2017-10-29T08:02:32+0000","source":{"provider":"wikipedia","name":"Wikimedia Commons","extern