m, a hotel, an outdoor amphitheatre, an observatory, and a few parks.\n\nThe district, likened to a city within a city, opened in 2003. Since then, it has managed to become one of the most prestigious addresses in Tokyo, with many leading IT companies having their offices here. \n\nAlthough still relatively new, Roppongi Hills has already managed to attract its share of controversy, too. Many citizens of Tokyo have protested the demolition of the old neighbourhood that preceded its construction and there have also been complaints about its excessively complicated layout. When visiting, do not forget to equip yourself with a good map or a GPS, as the area is often compared to a maze.","provider":null,"translation_provider":null,"link":null,"is_translated":true},"opening_hours_raw":null,"media_count":29,"main_media":{"usage":{"square":"m:2853646","video_preview":null,"portrait":"m:2853642","landscape":"m:2853646"},"media":[{"original":{"size":null,"width":2000,"height":1335},"suitability":["square","landscape"],"url_template":"https://media-cdn.sygictraveldata.com/media/{size}/612664395a40232133447d33247d3832383533363436","created_at":"2015-04-27T13:40:12+0000","source":{"provider":"wikipedia","name":"Wikimedia Commons","external_id":null},"type":"photo","created_by":"53d8a9428f8ff","url":"https://media-cdn.sygictraveldata.com/media/612664395a40232133447d33247d3832383533363436.jpg","quadkey":null,"attribution":{"title_url":"http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Beautiful_capital_-_Sony_A7R_(12096694564).jpg","license":"CC BY 2.0","other":null,"author_url":"http://www.flickr.com/people/23249662@N03","author":"Luke Ma","title":"City skyline Roppongi Hills Tokyo Japan 六本木 ヒルズ 東京 日本 by Sony A7R & FE 28-70mm F3.5-5.6 OSS","license_url":"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0"},"location":null,"id":"m:2853646"},{"original":{"size":null,"width":2288,"height":1712},"suitability":["portrait"],"url_template":"https://media-cdn.sygictraveldata.com/media/{size}/612664395a402